в”‚RustNet Monitor - Network Connection Monitor                                                      в”‚
в”‚                                                                                                  в”‚
в”‚q Quit application (press twice to confirm)                                                       в”‚
в”‚Ctrl+C Quit immediately                                                                           в”‚
в”‚x Clear all connections (press twice to confirm)                                                  в”‚
в”‚Tab Switch between tabs                                                                           в”‚
в”‚в†‘/k, в†“/j Navigate connections (wraps around)                                                      в”‚
в”‚g, G Jump to first/last connection (vim-style)                                                    в”‚
в”‚Page Up/Down, Ctrl+B/F Navigate connections by page                                               в”‚
в”‚c Copy remote address to clipboard                                                                в”‚
в”‚p Toggle between service names and port numbers                                                   в”‚
в”‚d Toggle between hostnames and IP addresses (when --resolve-dns)                                  в”‚
в”‚s Cycle through sort columns (Bandwidth, Process, etc.)                                           в”‚
в”‚S Toggle sort direction (ascending/descending)                                                    в”‚
в”‚a Toggle process grouping (aggregate by process)                                                  в”‚
в”‚Space Expand/collapse group (when grouping enabled)                                               в”‚
в”‚в†ђ/в†’ or h/l Collapse/expand group                                                                  в”‚
в”‚t Toggle display of historic (closed) connections                                                 в”‚
в”‚r Reset view (grouping, sort, filter)                                                             в”‚
в”‚Enter View connection details                                                                     в”‚
в”‚Esc Return to overview                                                                            в”‚
в”‚h Toggle this help screen                                                                         в”‚
в”‚i Toggle interface statistics view                                                                в”‚
в”‚/ Enter filter mode on Overview (use в†‘/в†“ to navigate while typing)                                в”‚
в”‚                                                                                                  в”‚
в”‚Tabs:                                                                                             в”‚
в”‚Overview Connection list with mini traffic graph                                                  в”‚
в”‚Details Full details for selected connection                                                      в”‚
