в”‚                                                                                                  в”‚
в”‚Mouse Controls:                                                                                   в”‚
в”‚Click tab Switch between tabs                                                                     в”‚
в”‚Click row Select connection                                                                       в”‚
в”‚Scroll wheel Navigate connection list                                                             в”‚
в”‚Double-click row Open connection details                                                          в”‚
в”‚Double-click group Expand/collapse process group                                                  в”‚
